<h1>What is this</h1>
<p>Small app using Sinatra and ruby-readability to make web articles easier to read when displaying in mobile apps.</p>
<h1>Usage</h1>
<p>http://readable.heroku.com/read/{full_url}<p>
<p>Example: http://readable.heroku.com/read/http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/03/05/connecticut.east.coast.rapist/index.html?hpt=T1</p>
